flowchart LR
    A[Intent and constraints] --> B[Human or agent planning]
    B --> C[Delegated objectives]
    C --> D[Generated and edited artifacts]
    D --> E[Review, policy, test, and simulation evidence]
    E --> F[Human acceptance or autonomous approval]
    F --> G[Deployment and operation]
    G --> H[User, business, reliability, and cost outcomes]
    H --> I[Correction, rollback, and organizational learning]
    I --> A

    P[Model, prompt, context, tools, permissions, and version provenance] -. attached to .-> B
    P -. attached to .-> C
    P -. attached to .-> D
    Q[Identity and delegation graph] -. explains responsibility .-> C
    Q -. explains responsibility .-> F
    R[Observed evidence] -. distinct from .-> S[Inference, simulation, and generated explanation]
    R --> E
    S --> E
